com.cboe.interfaces.domain.product
Interface PriceAdjustment

public interface PriceAdjustment

A change to the value of a security that affects the prices of derivative products related to it.

A PriceAdjustment is entered prior to the time that the products are changed. An adjustment must be applied for the affected products to be updated.
